										<br></br>
											<p>My name is Maria Christoforaki and (as of 2012-2013) I am a fourth year doctoral student in the Computer Science and Engineering Department of the <a href="http://www.poly.edu/" onClick="javascript: _gaq.push(['_trackPageview', 'to poly']);">Polytechnic Institute</a> of <a href="http://www.nyu.edu/" onClick="javascript: _gaq.push(['_trackPageview', 'to nyu']);">New York University</a>. </p>
											<p>I am working with Professor <a href="http://cis.poly.edu/suel/" onClick="javascript: _gaq.push(['_trackPageview', 'to torsten']);">Torsten Suel</a> and my research focus is in the areas of <b>Web Search</b>, <b>Information Retrieval</b>, and <b>Data Mining</b>. In particular, I am interested in studying and applying techniques of these areas in managing and analyzing <b>large scale datasets</b>.</p>
											<p>Before coming to NY I lived in  Greece, where I received my Diploma from the <a href="http://www.ceid.upatras.gr/en/index.htm" onClick="javascript: _gaq.push(['_trackPageview', 'to ceid']);">Computer Engineering and Informatics Department</a> of the University of Patras in 2009. My Diploma thesis advisors were Dr <a href="http://ru1.cti.gr/index.php/people/8-people/1-ichatz" onClick="javascript: _gaq.push(['_trackPageview', 'to ichatz']);">Ioannis Chatzigiannakis</a> and Professor <a href="http://ru1.cti.gr/Paul_Spirakis/" onClick="javascript: _gaq.push(['_trackPageview', 'to spyrakis']);">Paul Spirakis</a>.</p>
